### Dogs CRUD API - HTTP Requests Examples
### You can use this file with REST Client extension in VS Code

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@contentType = application/json

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Get all items
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/items

### Get item by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/items/1

### Create a new item
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/items
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Golden Retriever",
  "description": "Friendly and loyal dog breed"
}

### Create another item
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/items
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Labrador",
  "description": "Energetic and playful"
}

### Update an item
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/items/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Golden Retriever (Updated)",
  "description": "Very friendly and loyal dog breed"
}

### Update only name
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/items/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Golden Retriever v2"
}

### Delete an item
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/items/1

### Create multiple items in a transaction (batch)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/items/batch
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "items": [
    {
      "name": "Beagle",
      "description": "Small hunting dog"
    },
    {
      "name": "Bulldog",
      "description": "Muscular and wrinkled"
    },
    {
      "name": "Poodle",
      "description": "Intelligent and elegant"
    }
  ]
}

### Error case: Create item with duplicate name
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/items
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Golden Retriever"
}

### Error case: Create item without name
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/items
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "description": "No name provided"
}

### Error case: Get non-existent item
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/items/999999

### Error case: Invalid ID format
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/items/invalid-id

### Transaction rollback example
### This will fail because one item has a duplicate name
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/items/batch
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "items": [
    {
      "name": "Unique Dog 1"
    },
    {
      "name": "Golden Retriever"
    },
    {
      "name": "Unique Dog 2"
    }
  ]
}
